title: TDP-5 | Community Member of the Week | 2021-W37 | Yonks Family (Jason, Tyler, & Brooke)
body:
# Overview
Community Member of the Week (nomination / reward program) rewards 100 $RETOKEN.  Special exceptions can be made to expand this (IE: multiple people, etc).  This is a fun way that we recognize those that are building this community.

# 2021-W37 | Nominations
We like to nominate The Yonks Family, Jason, Tyler and Brooke for spearheading this group, being the leader that will lead our mission into fruition and for having the passion to create an open space for creatives that will make this community the dynamic energy that will change the world.
